MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_45_ME.pt: “Fique comigo e você estará em segurança.”
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_45_ME.th: "อยู่ใกล้ข้าไว้ แล้วท่านจะปลอดภัย.."
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_45_ME.vi: "Hãy bám sát theo ta và nàng sẽ an toàn."

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_460_M.en: Ngh... So this is the true strength of the Six Heroes combined...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_460_M.es: Ngh... So this is the true strength of the Six Heroes combined...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_460_M.id: Ngh… Jadi ini kekuatan sejati gabungan 6 Pahlawan…
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_460_M.pt: Ngh... So this is the true strength of the Six Heroes combined...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_460_M.th: โอย... นี่หรือคือความแข็งแกร่งที่แท้จริงของหกผู้กล้ารวมกัน...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_460_M.vi: Ngh... So this is the true strength of the Six Heroes combined...

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_461_M.en: Six Heroes. I understand your regret and anger.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_461_M.es: Six Heroes. I understand your regret and anger.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_461_M.id: Enam Pahlawan. Aku mengerti penyesalan dan murkamu.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_461_M.pt: Six Heroes. I understand your regret and anger.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_461_M.th: หกผู้กล้า ข้าเข้าใจถึงlสิ่งที่ค้างคาใจและความโกรธของพวกเจ้า
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_461_M.vi: Six Heroes. I understand your regret and anger.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_462_M.en: But I have to overcome you and continue forward!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_462_M.es: But I have to overcome you and continue forward!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_462_M.id: Tapi aku harus mengatasi kalian dan terus maju.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_462_M.pt: But I have to overcome you and continue forward!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_462_M.th: แต่ข้าจะต้องก้าวข้ามผ่านพวกเจ้าไปให้ได้และเดินหน้าต่อไป!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_462_M.vi: But I have to overcome you and continue forward!

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_463_M.en: Vargas, unlike me you continued to fight as a hero.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_463_M.es: Vargas, unlike me you continued to fight as a hero.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_463_M.id: Vargas, tidak seperti aku, kau terus bertarung sebagai pahlawan.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_463_M.pt: Vargas, unlike me you continued to fight as a hero.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_463_M.th: สาร์กัส ต่างกับข้า เจ้ายังคงต่อสู้ต่อไปในฐานะผู้กล้า
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_463_M.vi: Vargas, unlike me you continued to fight as a hero.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_464_M.en: That's why Tia and Lava's death hurt you so...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_464_M.es: That's why Tia and Lava's death hurt you so...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_464_M.id: Itulah mengapa kematian Tia dan Lava melukaimu...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_464_M.pt: That's why Tia and Lava's death hurt you so...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_464_M.th: นั่นเป็นเหตุผลว่าทำไม การตายของเทียกับลาวาถึงทำให้เจ้าเจ็บปวดใจยิ่งนัก...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_464_M.vi: That's why Tia and Lava's death hurt you so...

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_465_M.en: Farewell, Vargas. Unlike me, you were a hero to the very end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_465_M.es: Farewell, Vargas. Unlike me, you were a hero to the very end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_465_M.id: Selamat berpisah, Vargas. Tidak seperti aku, kau adalah pahlawan sampai akhir.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_465_M.pt: Farewell, Vargas. Unlike me, you were a hero to the very end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_465_M.th: ลาก่อน วาร์กัส ต่างกับข้า เจ้าคือผู้กล้าตราบจนวาระสุดท้าย
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_465_M.vi: Farewell, Vargas. Unlike me, you were a hero to the very end.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_466_M.en: Selena, I took everything from you to save the world.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_466_M.es: Selena, I took everything from you to save the world.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_466_M.id: Selena, aku mengambil semua darimu untuk menyelamatkan dunia.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_466_M.pt: Selena, I took everything from you to save the world.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_466_M.th: เซเลน่า ข้าเอาทุกๆ อย่างจากเจ้าไปเพื่อช่วยโลก
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_466_M.vi: Selena, I took everything from you to save the world.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_467_M.en: Even though I knew that small world is exactly what you wanted to protect...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_467_M.es: Even though I knew that small world is exactly what you wanted to protect...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_467_M.id: Meski aku tahu dunia kecil adalah yang ingin kau lindungi.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_467_M.pt: Even though I knew that small world is exactly what you wanted to protect...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_467_M.th: ถึงแม้ว่าข้าจะรู้อยู่แล้วว่าโลกใบเล็กนั่นแหละคือสิ่งที่เจ้าต้องการจะปกป้อง...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_467_M.vi: Even though I knew that small world is exactly what you wanted to protect...

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_468_M.en: Selena, even though you were called a hero, you wanted to live as a normal woman.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_468_M.es: Selena, even though you were called a hero, you wanted to live as a normal woman.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_468_M.id: Selena, meski kau disebut pahlawan, kau ingin hidup sebagai wanita normal.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_468_M.pt: Selena, even though you were called a hero, you wanted to live as a normal woman.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_468_M.th: เซเลน่า ถึงแม้เจ้าจะถูกเรียกว่าผู้กล้า เจ้าเองก็อยากจะใช้ชีวิตแบบผู้หญิงธรรมดา
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_468_M.vi: Selena, even though you were called a hero, you wanted to live as a normal woman.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_469_M.en: I'll never forget your final words.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_469_M.es: I'll never forget your final words.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_469_M.pt: I'll never forget your final words.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_469_M.th: ข้าจะไม่มีวันลืมคำพูดสุดท้ายของเจ้า
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_469_M.vi: I'll never forget your final words.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_470_M.en: Lance, the hero who didn't wish to be one. Did you tell yourself you were fighting for your friend?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_470_M.es: Lance, the hero who didn't wish to be one. Did you tell yourself you were fighting for your friend?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_470_M.id: Lance, pahlawan yang tidak ingin jadi pahlawan. Apa kau bilang ke diri sendiri kau bertarung untuk temanmu?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_470_M.pt: Lance, the hero who didn't wish to be one. Did you tell yourself you were fighting for your friend?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_470_M.th: แลนซ์ ผู้กล้าที่ไม่ได้ปรารถนาที่จะเป็นเลยสักนิด เจ้าบอกกับตัวเองว่าเจ้ากำลังต่อสู้เพื่อเพื่อนใช่ไหม?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_470_M.vi: Lance, the hero who didn't wish to be one. Did you tell yourself you were fighting for your friend?

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_471_M.th: ข้ามักจะอิจฉาเจ้าในเรื่องนั้น...

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_472_M.en: Were you finally able to meet your friend, Lance?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_472_M.es: Were you finally able to meet your friend, Lance?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_472_M.id: Apa kau akhirnya berhasil bertemu temanmu, Lance?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_472_M.pt: Were you finally able to meet your friend, Lance?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_472_M.th: สุดท้ายเจ้าสามารถไปพบเพื่อนของเจ้าได้ไหรือไม่ แลนซ์?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_472_M.vi: Were you finally able to meet your friend, Lance?

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_473_M.en: No, I believe you did. I know in my heart you were able to meet them.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_473_M.es: No, I believe you did. I know in my heart you were able to meet them.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_473_M.id: Tidak, aku percaya kau bertemu. Aku, tahu dalam hatiku, kau bisa bertemu mereka.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_473_M.pt: No, I believe you did. I know in my heart you were able to meet them.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_473_M.th: ไม่ เข้าเชื่อว่าเจ้าได้ทำไปแล้ว ข้ารู้ในหัวใจว่าเจ้าสามารถไปพบพวกเขาได้
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_473_M.vi: No, I believe you did. I know in my heart you were able to meet them.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_474_M.en: Eze, your strength remained a constant until the very end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_474_M.es: Eze, your strength remained a constant until the very end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_474_M.id: Eze, kekuatanmu tetap sama sampai akhir.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_474_M.pt: Eze, your strength remained a constant until the very end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_474_M.th: อีเซ่ ความแข็งแกร่งของเจ้ายังคงมั่นตราบจนวาระสุดท้าย
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_474_M.vi: Eze, your strength remained a constant until the very end.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_475_M.th: เจ้าคือผู้กล้าอย่างแท้จริง

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_476_M.en: The strength to choose death with a smile. Eze, you were so cool, all the way to the end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_476_M.es: The strength to choose death with a smile. Eze, you were so cool, all the way to the end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_476_M.id: Kekuatan untuk memilih mati dengan tersenyum. Eze, kau keren sekali sampai akhir.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_476_M.pt: The strength to choose death with a smile. Eze, you were so cool, all the way to the end.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_476_M.th: ความแข็งแกร่งที่เลือกความตายด้วยรอยยิ้ม อีเซ่ เจ้าช่างสุดยอดจนถึงวาระสุดท้าย
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_476_M.vi: The strength to choose death with a smile. Eze, you were so cool, all the way to the end.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_477_M.en: Atro. You raged against it even though you understood everything.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_477_M.es: Atro. You raged against it even though you understood everything.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_477_M.id: Atro. Kau murka meski kau memahami segalanya.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_477_M.pt: Atro. You raged against it even though you understood everything.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_477_M.th: อาโทร เจ้าค้านหัวชนฝาแม้ว่าเจ้าจะเข้าใจทุกๆ อย่าง
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_477_M.vi: Atro. You raged against it even though you understood everything.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_478_M.en: What was your anger directed at? Was it me, the gods, or the whole world?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_478_M.es: What was your anger directed at? Was it me, the gods, or the whole world?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_478_M.id: Kau marah pada siapa? Aku, dewa, atau seluruh dunia?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_478_M.pt: What was your anger directed at? Was it me, the gods, or the whole world?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_478_M.th: ความโกรธของเจ้านั้นพาเจ้าไปทางไหน? ที่ข้า เทพเจ้า หรือโลกทั้งใบ?
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_478_M.vi: What was your anger directed at? Was it me, the gods, or the whole world?

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_479_M.en: Atro, it was because of your consideration of others even in the face of an unjust death...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_479_M.es: Atro, it was because of your consideration of others even in the face of an unjust death...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_479_M.id: Atro, karena pertimbanganmu untuk orang lain, bahkan saat menghadapi kematian yang tidak adil…
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_479_M.pt: Atro, it was because of your consideration of others even in the face of an unjust death...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_479_M.th: อาโทร เพราะความใส่ใจผู้อื่นของเจ้า แม้ว่าจะต้องเผชิญหน้ากับความตายที่ไม่อาจเลี่ยงได้...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_479_M.vi: Atro, it was because of your consideration of others even in the face of an unjust death...

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_47_ME.en: "Thank you Xenon. For all your thoughtful protection after we fled the kingdom."
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_47_ME.es: Gracias, Xenon. Por ser tan amable y protegerme después de huir del reino.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_47_ME.id: "Terima kasih, Xenon. Untuk semua perlindunganmu setelah kita keluar dari istana."
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_47_ME.pt: “Obrigado, Xenon. Por ter me protegido com tanto cuidado depois de fugirmos do reino.”
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_47_ME.th: "ขอบใจนะซีน่อน สำหรับการเอาใจใส่ปกป้องข้าตั้งแต่เราหนีออกมาจากราชอาณาจักร"
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_47_ME.vi: "Cảm ơn anh Xenon. Vì tất cả sự bảo vệ chu đáo của anh sau khi chúng ta rời bỏ vương quốc."

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_480_M.en: ...that my friend, Kuda, was saved. At this time I come not to apologize, but to thank you.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_480_M.es: ...that my friend, Kuda, was saved. At this time I come not to apologize, but to thank you.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_480_M.id: …temanku, Kuda, jadi selamat. Saat ini aku datang bukan untuk meminta maaf, namun untuk berterima kasih.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_480_M.pt: ...that my friend, Kuda, was saved. At this time I come not to apologize, but to thank you.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_480_M.th: ...นั่นเพื่อนข้า คุดะ ที่ถูกช่วยไว้ ในเวลานี้ ข้าไม่ได้มาเพื่อขอให้ยกโทษ แต่มาเพื่อขอบคุณ
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_480_M.vi: ...that my friend, Kuda, was saved. At this time I come not to apologize, but to thank you.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_481_M.en: Magress, the knight of rage and madness. At first I thought you were the farthest thing from a hero.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_481_M.es: Magress, the knight of rage and madness. At first I thought you were the farthest thing from a hero.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_481_M.id: Magress, ksatria murka dan gila. Pertamanya kukira kau sangat jauh dari sosok pahlawan.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_481_M.pt: Magress, the knight of rage and madness. At first I thought you were the farthest thing from a hero.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_481_M.th: มาเกรส อัศวินแห่งความพิโรธและบ้าคลั่ง ในตอนแรกข้าคิดว่าเจ้านั้นช่างห่างไกลจากคำว่าผูเกล้ามากที่สุด
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_481_M.vi: Magress, the knight of rage and madness. At first I thought you were the farthest thing from a hero.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_482_M.en: I had no qualms about killing you. But, you were different...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_482_M.es: I had no qualms about killing you. But, you were different...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_482_M.id: Aku tidak ragu membunuhmu. Namun kau berbeda…
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_482_M.pt: I had no qualms about killing you. But, you were different...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_482_M.th: ข้าไม่มีรู้สึกอะไรเลยสักนิดหากต้องฆ่าเจ้า แต่ เข้านั้นต่างออกไป...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_482_M.vi: I had no qualms about killing you. But, you were different...

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_483_M.en: Magress, while hiding that madness within, you had the strength of a true knight.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_483_M.es: Magress, while hiding that madness within, you had the strength of a true knight.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_483_M.id: Magress, bersembunyi dalam kegilaan, kau memiliki kekuatan ksatria sejati.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_483_M.pt: Magress, while hiding that madness within, you had the strength of a true knight.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_483_M.th: มาเกรส ข้าที่ซ่อนความบ้าคลั่งไว้ภายใน เจ้ามีความแข็งแกร่งของอัศวินที่แท้จริง
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_483_M.vi: Magress, while hiding that madness within, you had the strength of a true knight.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_484_M.en: I knew from the way you fought. That you had the nobility of a true knight.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_484_M.es: I knew from the way you fought. That you had the nobility of a true knight.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_484_M.id: Aku tahu dari caramu bertarung. Kau punya kemuliaan ksatria sejati.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_484_M.pt: I knew from the way you fought. That you had the nobility of a true knight.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_484_M.th: ข้ารู้จากวิธีที่เจ้าต่อสู้ เจ้ามีเกียรติของอัศวินที่แท้จริง
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_484_M.vi: I knew from the way you fought. That you had the nobility of a true knight.

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_485_M.en: Grh... So you can't forgive me...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_485_M.es: Grh... So you can't forgive me...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_485_M.id: Grh... Jadi kau tak dapat memaafkanku...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_485_M.pt: Grh... So you can't forgive me...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_485_M.th: หึ... เจ้าอภัยให้ข้าไม่ได้สินะ...
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_485_M.vi: Grh... So you can't forgive me...

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_486_M.en: I feel Ilia's presence... I feel that, now...I can seal the evil power! Believe in my strength!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_486_M.es: I feel Ilia's presence... I feel that, now...I can seal the evil power! Believe in my strength!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_486_M.id: Aku merasakan kehadiran Ilia… Aku merasakan itu sekarang… Aku bisa menyegel kekuatan jahat! Percayalah pada kekuatanku!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_486_M.pt: I feel Ilia's presence... I feel that, now...I can seal the evil power! Believe in my strength!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_486_M.th: ข้าสัมผัสได้ถึงอิเลีย... ข้ารู้สึกถึงได้, ตอนนี้...ข้าสามารถผนึกพลังที่ชั่วร้ายได้! เชื่อมั่นในพลังของข้า!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_486_M.vi: I feel Ilia's presence... I feel that, now...I can seal the evil power! Believe in my strength!

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_487_M.en: I'll bring it all to an end! We'll give all we have and see it through to the end!!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_487_M.es: I'll bring it all to an end! We'll give all we have and see it through to the end!!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_487_M.id: Akan kuakhiri semua! Kita akan memberikan semua yang kita punya dan menyaksikan sampai akhir!!
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_487_M.pt: I'll bring it all to an end! We'll give all we have and see it through to the end!!

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_55_ME.en: "All is of my duty, and I will stay with you till we find peace."
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_55_ME.es: Todo es parte de mi deber, y me quedaré contigo hasta que encontremos la paz.
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_55_ME.id: "Semua adalah tugas saya, dan saya akan bersama Anda sampai kita menemukan kedamaian."
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_55_ME.pt: “Isso é parte do meu dever e ficarei com você até encontrarmos a paz.”
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_55_ME.th: "ทั้งหมดมันเป็นหน้าที่ของข้าอยู่แล้ว และข้าจะอยู่กับท่านจนกว่าเราทั้งคู่จะพบกับความสงบสุข"
MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_55_ME.vi: "Tất cả là nhiệm vụ của ta và ta sẽ ở bên nàng cho đến khi chúng ta tìm thấy hòa bình."

MST_MISSIONSCRIPT_COMMANDPARAMETER_574_M.pt:
